{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给罗驭雄的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给罗驭的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年4月19日）驭雄学兄教席："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月十四日大示敬悉，深感盛意。所指干部中的缺点错误，所在多有，必须整饰。倘有所见，尚祈随时示知。来京一节，似可从缓，工作或学习均以就近从事为宜，未审尊意以为然否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此复，敬颂教安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年四月十九日[1]罗驭雄，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":4,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":294,"page_end":294},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}